  "description": {
    "zh": "你好呀，朋友！最近怎么样？我倒是一切都好。说实在的，感觉日子有点过于舒服了。哎呀，总不能凡尔赛，对吧！\n\n我再也没法在旧厂房里玩俄罗斯方块了，已经回不去了。所以我找了一个新的，大大的游乐场。但是那里还没有任何设施！\n\n我想要用工厂里剩下的东西，自己做一台叉车。那里的东西应该足够我拼出一辆了。你不用收集零件，只用帮我的手下们规划一下路线就好。",
    "en": "Hello, friend! How are you doing? Things are going well for me here. Sometimes it even seems too good to be true. Well, can't complain though!\n\nI can't play Tetriz in the old warehouse anymore, so I've found a new, bigger playground. But there's no machinery! \n\nI want to build myself a forklift from what's left in the factory. There should be enough surviving parts for one. You don't have to collect parts, just route my men through all the forklifts."
  },
